{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant\/data","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant\/VariantProtocol-Implementations"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a pointer to the serialized form of a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The returned data may not be in fully-normalised form if read from an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"untrusted source.  The returned data must not be freed; it remains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"valid for as long as "},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" exists.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:4GLib15VariantProtocolPAAE4dataSVSgvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib7VariantC","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"symbolKind":"property","extendedModule":"GLib","role":"symbol","title":"data","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gconstpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gconstpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/variant\/data"]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gconstpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gconstpointer"},{"text":"? { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" is a fixed-sized value that was deserialized from a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"corrupted serialized container then ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" may be returned.  In this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"case, the proper thing to do is typically to use the appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"number of nul bytes in place of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":".  If "},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not fixed-sized"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"then "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" is never returned."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In the case that ","type":"text"},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is already in serialized form, this function","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"O(1)"},{"type":"text","text":".  If the value is not already in serialized form,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"serialization occurs implicitly and is approximately "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"O(n)"},{"type":"text","text":" in the size"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the result."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To deserialize the data returned by this function, in addition to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"serialized data, you must know the type of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", and (if the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"machine might be different) the endianness of the machine that stored","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it. As a result, file formats or network messages that incorporate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"serialized ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GVariants"},{"type":"text","text":" must include this information either"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implicitly (for instance “the file always contains a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_VARIANT_TYPE_VARIANT"},{"type":"text","text":" and it is always in little-endian order”) or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"explicitly (by storing the type and\/or endianness in addition to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"serialized data)."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Variant":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Variant"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"Variant","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GVariant"},{"type":"text","text":" is a variant datatype; it can contain one or more values"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"along with information about the type of the values."}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variant","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Variant","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Variant/VariantProtocol-Implementations":{"role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant\/VariantProtocol-Implementations","type":"topic","title":"VariantProtocol Implementations","kind":"article","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variant\/variantprotocol-implementations"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Variant/data":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant\/data","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"